cursor.execute("Delete from restaurant")
#Inserting data in User Table:- 
for index,row in restaurant_df.iterrows():
    cursor.execute("INSERT INTO restaurant values (%s,%s,%s,%s,%s,%s,%s,%s,%s,%s,%s,%s,%s)", (int(row['restaurant_id']),row['restaurant_name'],row['restaurant_rating'],row['restaurant_type'],row['restaurant_contact_no'],row['opening_hrs'],row['closing_hrs'],row['budget_for_2'],row['restaurant_address'],row['city'],row['state'],row['zipcode'],row['no_of_tables']))
conn.commit()

cursor.execute("SELECT * from restaurant")
records=cursor.fetchall()
print(records)
conn.commit()

cursor.execute("Delete from cuisine")
#Inserting data in User Table:- 
for index,row in cuisine_df.iterrows():
    cursor.execute("INSERT INTO cuisine values (%s,%s)", (int(row['cuisine_id']),row['cuisine_name']))
conn.commit()

cursor.execute("SELECT * from cuisine")
records=cursor.fetchall()
print(records)
conn.commit()

cursor.execute("Delete from restaurant_dishes")
#Inserting data in User Table:- 
for index,row in dishes_df.iterrows():
    cursor.execute("INSERT INTO restaurant_dishes values (%s,%s,%s,%s,%s,%s,%s)", (int(row['dish_id']),row['restaurant_id'],row['dish_name'],row['dish_type'],row['dish_price'],row['cuisine_id'],row['menu_id']))
conn.commit()

cursor.execute("SELECT * from restaurant_dishes")
records=cursor.fetchall()
print(records)
conn.commit()

In [25]:
cursor.execute("Delete from restaurant_review")
#Inserting data in User Table:- 
for index,row in review_df.iterrows():
    cursor.execute("INSERT INTO restaurant_review values (%s,%s,%s,%s,%s,%s,%s)", (int(row['review_id']),row['review_comment'],row['review_likes'],row['user_rating'],row['date_posted'],row['restaurant_id'],row['user_id']))
conn.commit()

cursor.execute("SELECT * from restaurant_review")
records=cursor.fetchall()
print(records)
conn.commit()

cursor.execute("Delete from restaurant_reservation")
#Inserting data in User Table:- 
for index,row in reservation_df.iterrows():
    cursor.execute("INSERT INTO restaurant_reservation values (%s,%s,%s,%s,%s,%s)", (int(row['reservation_id']),row['no of people'],row['time '],row['date'],row['restaurant_id'],row['user_id']))
conn.commit()

cursor.execute("SELECT * from restaurant_reservation")
records=cursor.fetchall()
print(records)
conn.commit()

cursor.execute("Delete from restaurant_cancellation")
#Inserting data in User Table:- 
for index,row in cancellation_df.iterrows():
    cursor.execute("INSERT INTO restaurant_cancellation values (%s,%s,%s,%s)", (int(row['cancellation_id']),row['Cancellation reason'],row['restaurant_id'],row['user_id']))
conn.commit()
